                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18411213-328-offence-1 t18411213-cd-28"></join>7th of December</rs>, 3 pairs of socks, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18411213-name-193" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18411213-name-193" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
