                        <interp inst="t18411213-name-195" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS CROSSMAN</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable E</hi> 27.) I took the prisoner, and found these socks on him at the station.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
